1
00:00:54,886 --> 00:00:56,686
Will she come?
- I don't know.

2
00:01:01,246 --> 00:01:02,406
How much is this bike?

3
00:01:03,246 --> 00:01:04,403
Dad bought it for me.

4
00:01:05,206 --> 00:01:06,446
Sir, she is here.

5
00:01:21,243 --> 00:01:23,966
Hi.
- Hi.

6
00:01:33,563 --> 00:01:34,446
Hi.

7
00:01:35,886 --> 00:01:38,086
What is this, Joji?
You're looking really smart.

8
00:01:38,383 --> 00:01:40,926
Love your outfit.
- Really?

9
00:01:42,646 --> 00:01:43,523
Thank you.

10
00:01:44,566 --> 00:01:46,806
Okay, enough of your shyness.

11
00:01:47,283 --> 00:01:50,046
Someone might see us.
Start the bike quickly.

12
00:01:50,203 --> 00:01:51,446
Shall we go?
- Let's go.

13
00:01:52,886 --> 00:01:54,803
Shall I sit?
Will you ride it?

14
00:01:54,923 --> 00:01:56,795
Do you remember what I said?
You didn't forget, right?

15
00:01:56,843 --> 00:01:58,926
I remember it very well.
- Ride carefully.

16
00:02:00,843 --> 00:02:05,686
Sir.. Compliment her dress.

17
00:02:06,419 --> 00:02:08,579
Say that her dress is good.
- What?

18
00:02:08,710 --> 00:02:10,886
Compliment her outfit.
- Oh..

19
00:02:11,758 --> 00:02:12,592
Padma.

20
00:02:14,052 --> 00:02:15,732
Your dress is beautiful.

21
00:02:15,903 --> 00:02:17,766
Okay.
- Looking marvellous.

22
00:02:17,863 --> 00:02:21,566
Okay, thank you. Start the bike
first. Someone might see us.

23
00:02:21,685 --> 00:02:23,045
Okay, hold on tight.

24
00:02:23,503 --> 00:02:27,366
Bye.
- Bye. - Bye..

25
00:02:37,853 --> 00:02:42,886
I think your father is next.
- Run now. I might lash out.

26
00:02:43,243 --> 00:02:45,726
How many days
will he eat by himself?

27
00:02:45,973 --> 00:02:47,326
He will deal with that.

28
00:02:49,283 --> 00:02:50,763
In his old days..

29
00:02:51,166 --> 00:02:55,086
Will you shut up for a while?
Always talking non-stop.

30
00:02:55,966 --> 00:02:58,606
If you keep talking,
I'll get really mad.

31
00:02:59,533 --> 00:03:01,686
I have already given
the bike trusting you.

32
00:03:02,323 --> 00:03:04,683
If anything happens to my bike..

33
00:03:06,686 --> 00:03:07,566
Move.

34
00:03:12,402 --> 00:03:13,682
It's good if they're happy.

35
00:03:21,686 --> 00:03:26,366
Riya, I have taken many
wrong decisions in your life.

36
00:03:27,566 --> 00:03:31,846
Not only that, I have
not saved you from that.

37
00:03:33,573 --> 00:03:35,606
Dad, you..

38
00:03:36,246 --> 00:03:38,486
Tell me, dear,
what are you thinking?

39
00:03:43,206 --> 00:03:46,966
If I speak from my heart,
I will start crying.

40
00:03:48,086 --> 00:03:50,286
All these days,
I have cried enough.

41
00:03:50,806 --> 00:03:52,723
Correct, I am also saying the same.

42
00:03:52,943 --> 00:03:55,100
You have cried enough.
Hereafter, you should not cry.

43
00:03:55,806 --> 00:03:56,806
You should be happy.

44
00:03:58,766 --> 00:04:00,686
As the owner of such a big resort,

45
00:04:01,566 --> 00:04:06,006
I feared people might judge
my daughter being a divorcee.

46
00:04:06,486 --> 00:04:07,606
That's what was on my mind.

47
00:04:08,566 --> 00:04:12,406
But hereafter, only your
happiness is important to me.

48
00:04:12,686 --> 00:04:14,523
Nothing else is important
to me other than you.

49
00:04:15,606 --> 00:04:19,926
I am not worried about what
society and others might think.

50
00:04:20,566 --> 00:04:21,966
I am telling you now.

51
00:04:23,006 --> 00:04:26,446
Just divorce Deepak.

52
00:04:30,445 --> 00:04:34,246
He has been so toxic!
I'm sorry, dear.

53
00:04:34,963 --> 00:04:38,406
I am responsible
for everything. Sorry.

54
00:04:39,366 --> 00:04:40,603
Dad, I am also sorry.

55
00:04:41,157 --> 00:04:44,357
For not telling you
that I'm pregnant.

56
00:04:45,523 --> 00:04:47,963
I should have told you, but..
- It's okay.

57
00:04:48,886 --> 00:04:51,046
Hereafter, you should
not worry about anything.

58
00:04:51,486 --> 00:04:55,206
You should believe that
I am here to take care of you.

59
00:04:55,926 --> 00:05:00,086
I am there, dear. I will take
care of you and the baby.

60
00:05:00,526 --> 00:05:01,966
Come with me.

61
00:05:02,966 --> 00:05:05,086
No, Dad, it's okay.

62
00:05:05,303 --> 00:05:07,726
What, dear?
What are you saying? Come on.

63
00:05:28,371 --> 00:05:29,708
Sir, I'm sorry.

64
00:05:29,783 --> 00:05:32,566
I spoke harshly
in the meeting the other day.

65
00:05:32,783 --> 00:05:35,406
I should not have spoken like that.
- What is this, Nedumaran?

66
00:05:35,883 --> 00:05:36,966
Don't I know about you?

67
00:05:37,286 --> 00:05:38,966
I've been seeing you
since your training period.

68
00:05:39,405 --> 00:05:41,325
If you are angry,
it is justified.

69
00:05:41,403 --> 00:05:45,283
No, sir, you are not talking to me
since you came. - No..

70
00:05:45,803 --> 00:05:47,326
I got to know

71
00:05:47,803 --> 00:05:52,086
that Riya is pregnant
only at the party.

72
00:05:52,486 --> 00:05:55,686
I felt very bad
when she hid it from me.

73
00:05:56,203 --> 00:06:00,323
I got to know it
like a third person at the party.

74
00:06:00,846 --> 00:06:02,966
So what place do I hold
in Riya's heart?

75
00:06:03,531 --> 00:06:07,211
How much does Riya love me?
I've been thinking about it.

76
00:06:07,323 --> 00:06:10,326
Sir, please don't think like that.

77
00:06:10,886 --> 00:06:13,006
I have known Riya
since her childhood.

78
00:06:14,163 --> 00:06:18,243
Only she knows what she is facing.

79
00:06:18,446 --> 00:06:19,686
Excuse me, sir.

80
00:06:30,225 --> 00:06:31,926
You've got to control yourself, sir.
- I'll take this.

81
00:06:32,477 --> 00:06:33,772
I can't.

82
00:06:34,246 --> 00:06:36,443
That's why I asked them
to reduce the sugar.

83
00:06:36,646 --> 00:06:38,206
Cut it totally, sir.

84
00:06:52,446 --> 00:06:54,926
Sir, don't eat it.

85
00:06:55,483 --> 00:06:58,046
Sir, there is a lot of sugar in it.

86
00:07:06,219 --> 00:07:08,992
No, sir, it's very high..

87
00:07:10,974 --> 00:07:12,094
How did you know this?

88
00:07:12,223 --> 00:07:15,683
Sir, when you opened it,
I smelled a strong scent of sugar.

89
00:07:16,046 --> 00:07:17,203
I told you based on that.

90
00:07:18,923 --> 00:07:19,926
Okay.

91
00:07:20,806 --> 00:07:24,363
Sir, but I swear I didn't taste it.
- No..

92
00:07:25,366 --> 00:07:27,166
I didn't think
you would have done that.

93
00:07:27,343 --> 00:07:29,626
But, I was wondering if you can tell

94
00:07:29,674 --> 00:07:32,286
the amount of sugar
just from the smell.

95
00:07:32,603 --> 00:07:33,966
Maran, is it possible?

96
00:07:35,403 --> 00:07:38,966
Actually you can't smell
sugar, sir. You can't.

97
00:07:40,643 --> 00:07:42,603
But, you can smell caramel. Yeah.

98
00:07:42,926 --> 00:07:46,006
I think he smelt
the caramel and he..

99
00:07:46,323 --> 00:07:50,406
It's not possible
to smell sugar, sir..

100
00:07:50,763 --> 00:07:54,966
Very few people can do it.

101
00:07:55,883 --> 00:07:57,326
He is..

102
00:07:59,603 --> 00:08:00,486
Maran.

103
00:08:01,486 --> 00:08:04,286
Are you okay?
- Yeah..

104
00:08:04,403 --> 00:08:06,886
I am okay, sir, I am okay.

105
00:08:07,523 --> 00:08:11,406
You've served it, right? Take this
and clear it. - Okay, sir.

106
00:08:11,493 --> 00:08:14,510
Ask the person who prepared
it to wait in my room. - Okay, sir.

107
00:08:15,323 --> 00:08:16,566
Get out.

108
00:08:21,886 --> 00:08:27,163
Good guy. He was the one-day
chef, right? - Yes, sir, yes.

109
00:08:27,246 --> 00:08:32,406
Maran, why don't you add him
to the kitchen team and train him?

110
00:08:32,653 --> 00:08:34,773
Sir, it doesn't work like that.

111
00:08:35,526 --> 00:08:39,886
You need basic book knowledge to
follow a recipe and work as a chef.

112
00:08:40,446 --> 00:08:43,483
He is not educated, sir. No.

113
00:08:44,723 --> 00:08:48,766
Maran, how did
our Chidambaram come to us?

114
00:08:49,013 --> 00:08:51,486
What was his education?
What was his book knowledge?

115
00:08:52,126 --> 00:08:55,726
You don't want me to remind you
about Chidambaram's cooking, right?

116
00:08:57,046 --> 00:08:58,486
Sir, Chidambaram..

117
00:08:59,406 --> 00:09:02,393
You know what
Chidambaram did to us, sir.

118
00:09:02,966 --> 00:09:05,713
Why are you talking about it now?
- Okay..

119
00:09:06,206 --> 00:09:08,613
That's your wish.
You have to take a call on that.

120
00:09:08,730 --> 00:09:11,803
I told you what I wanted to tell.

121
00:09:12,046 --> 00:09:14,086
But, I lost an ice cream.

122
00:09:14,806 --> 00:09:17,646
Nedumaran, you have to prepare
an ice cream for me.

123
00:09:18,493 --> 00:09:19,926
Yeah, sure, sir.

124
00:09:31,366 --> 00:09:32,726
Hey, what is this?

125
00:09:33,326 --> 00:09:35,286
Why have you charged me
for the dishes that I didn't eat?

126
00:09:35,803 --> 00:09:39,043
I'm already angry about the
price increase at your resort.

127
00:09:39,406 --> 00:09:42,723
Now, you have wrongly
charged me Rs. 550.

128
00:09:44,566 --> 00:09:45,806
What are you glaring at?

129
00:09:46,406 --> 00:09:49,046
You ate the Chicken Burrito
and charged it to my bill?

130
00:09:49,886 --> 00:09:51,886
Why would I do that, bro?
- Bro?

131
00:09:52,243 --> 00:09:54,806
Who is your bro?
Am I your bro?

132
00:09:55,163 --> 00:09:56,046
Sorry, sir.

133
00:09:57,046 --> 00:09:58,646
Such issues are normal in billing.

134
00:09:58,963 --> 00:10:00,766
Just give me 10 minutes,
I will sort this out.

135
00:10:00,886 --> 00:10:01,966
Do you think you're a big shot?

136
00:10:02,062 --> 00:10:03,640
You talk in English
as if you're a hotshot.

137
00:10:03,688 --> 00:10:05,903
Did I speak to you in English?
I spoke to you in Tamil, right?

138
00:10:05,963 --> 00:10:07,926
Similarly, you should
talk to me in Tamil, right?

139
00:10:08,366 --> 00:10:10,486
Sorry, sir.
Forgive me, sir.

140
00:10:10,723 --> 00:10:14,726
Give me 10 minutes. I will
change the bill and come. - Go..

141
00:10:31,966 --> 00:10:33,923
I feel bad thinking about him.

142
00:10:34,846 --> 00:10:36,166
Even I feel bad.

143
00:10:36,766 --> 00:10:40,046
But, when I talk to him,
he talks in a way that I feel worse.

144
00:10:41,643 --> 00:10:42,872
Poor guy.

145
00:10:43,419 --> 00:10:47,323
He is short-tempered. If we
control that, he will be fine.

146
00:10:47,886 --> 00:10:50,683
Believe in something impossible.
- No, Aishu.

147
00:10:51,006 --> 00:10:53,766
Once he comes to the kitchen after
the punishment, he will be fine.

148
00:10:55,686 --> 00:11:00,206
But, when he works in room service,
the guests will treat him badly.

149
00:11:00,766 --> 00:11:03,526
I don't know how
he is going to handle that.

150
00:11:03,926 --> 00:11:06,443
Why are you thinking about that?
Don't think about it.

151
00:11:07,502 --> 00:11:09,382
I can't stop thinking about it.

152
00:11:09,872 --> 00:11:11,712
Something is
constantly bothering me.

153
00:11:12,257 --> 00:11:13,457
Don't get tense.

154
00:11:14,046 --> 00:11:17,003
He should understand all this.
- No, Aishu. - Let's see.

155
00:11:17,083 --> 00:11:18,846
Who billed for room number 210?

156
00:11:24,883 --> 00:11:26,923
I did. What happened?

157
00:11:27,286 --> 00:11:28,446
What are you thinking, Veni?

158
00:11:28,966 --> 00:11:30,646
Haven't I had enough?

159
00:11:31,126 --> 00:11:33,326
You have added a Chicken Burrito
that he did not order, to his bill.

160
00:11:33,886 --> 00:11:36,006
He is talking as if I am a thief.

161
00:11:37,286 --> 00:11:39,743
Humiliate me all you want.

162
00:11:40,166 --> 00:11:41,886
What are you thinking?

163
00:11:42,363 --> 00:11:44,246
Mistakes do happen while billing.

164
00:11:44,926 --> 00:11:48,003
You are talking as if you never
made a mistake while billing.

165
00:11:48,286 --> 00:11:49,406
Yes, Sous chef.

166
00:11:49,723 --> 00:11:52,606
Why are you getting
involved in such cheap things?

167
00:11:53,043 --> 00:11:56,723
Go and mind your own business.
-That's exactly what I'm doing.

168
00:11:56,907 --> 00:11:58,806
Why are you shouting like this?

169
00:11:59,603 --> 00:12:02,526
Are you happy to see me
shouting like a dog?

170
00:12:03,366 --> 00:12:04,926
Don't talk like a fool, Vicky.

171
00:12:05,086 --> 00:12:08,006
I can't even enter
the kitchen in this shirt.

172
00:12:08,166 --> 00:12:09,486
I'll look like a fool indeed.

173
00:12:11,726 --> 00:12:12,686
Take this.

174
00:12:15,028 --> 00:12:16,948
Make someone else deal with this.

175
00:12:17,726 --> 00:12:18,686
He is here.

176
00:12:19,241 --> 00:12:21,321
He must have faced many issues.
So, make him deal with it.

177
00:12:22,206 --> 00:12:23,286
What happened?

178
00:12:23,511 --> 00:12:24,966
Joji has been
admitted to a hospital.

179
00:12:25,326 --> 00:12:26,526
What are you saying?

180
00:12:26,853 --> 00:12:28,873
Wait, I will be back. Stay here.
- Okay.

181
00:12:29,653 --> 00:12:30,963
Come fast.
- Grace..

182
00:12:31,033 --> 00:12:32,963
An emergency.
Can you give me your bike key?

183
00:12:34,113 --> 00:12:36,566
I am going to the entrance.
- Bike key? - Bike Key.

184
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:38,559
I am coming, you go.
- Here you go.

185
00:12:46,106 --> 00:12:48,386
There is an old man named Joji..
- Go straight and take right.

186
00:12:48,446 --> 00:12:50,406
Here? How..
- Thank you.

187
00:13:00,574 --> 00:13:03,217
Hey, Vetri, come in.
- What happened, sir?

188
00:13:03,966 --> 00:13:05,646
Nothing.
- What happened, Doctor?

189
00:13:07,126 --> 00:13:08,646
Sudden spike in blood sugar.

190
00:13:10,333 --> 00:13:13,333
Because of that,
his BP also fluctuated.

191
00:13:13,846 --> 00:13:15,806
So, please don't give him sugar.

192
00:13:16,563 --> 00:13:19,086
So, don't worry.
Nothing to panic about.

193
00:13:19,603 --> 00:13:23,206
He needs proper diet
control and rest. - Okay, Doctor.

194
00:13:23,638 --> 00:13:24,517
Phew.

195
00:13:24,606 --> 00:13:27,366
Don't allow him to eat
any sugary food.

196
00:13:28,606 --> 00:13:31,039
That's the reason for all this.
- Oh, no..

197
00:13:33,023 --> 00:13:34,463
What did you find out now?

198
00:13:37,126 --> 00:13:39,126
I got to know that he has diabetes.

199
00:13:39,726 --> 00:13:41,483
You were listening
as if you understood everything.

200
00:13:42,073 --> 00:13:44,770
He was putting in effort
to explain. That's why..

201
00:13:45,606 --> 00:13:48,286
His blood sugar had hiked
after eating something. Ask him.

202
00:13:49,326 --> 00:13:51,003
What happened, sir?

203
00:13:51,363 --> 00:13:54,043
Tell me now.
- Nothing, Vetri. - Nothing?

204
00:13:54,366 --> 00:13:56,523
Did you faint for no reason?
- Leave that.

205
00:13:57,646 --> 00:13:58,806
I won't. Tell me.

206
00:13:59,843 --> 00:14:02,163
That is..

207
00:14:02,246 --> 00:14:04,246
Padma said she likes brownies.

208
00:14:05,886 --> 00:14:08,046
I bought it for her.
- Okay.

209
00:14:09,126 --> 00:14:10,606
I didn't ask her.

210
00:14:11,726 --> 00:14:14,766
She fed it to me.

211
00:14:16,775 --> 00:14:19,095
I had it under control
for so many years.

212
00:14:20,003 --> 00:14:23,283
When she fed me,
I couldn't control myself.

213
00:14:24,006 --> 00:14:25,166
So, I ate it.

214
00:14:26,606 --> 00:14:28,503
I got to know when I saw it.

215
00:14:28,883 --> 00:14:30,646
There was a lot of sugar in it.

216
00:14:32,646 --> 00:14:35,006
I didn't want to eat it.
- Okay.

217
00:14:35,446 --> 00:14:39,046
Then, the things that shouldn't
have happened, happened.

218
00:14:44,006 --> 00:14:46,406
No, Vetri, it's the first time..

219
00:14:46,726 --> 00:14:48,886
When she gave it to me,

220
00:14:49,166 --> 00:14:51,766
it did not seem nice to say
that I am diabetic, right?

221
00:14:51,883 --> 00:14:54,846
Of course..
- Think about it.

222
00:14:58,883 --> 00:15:01,606
Hey, my bike is fine, right?

223
00:15:03,543 --> 00:15:05,566
I'm admitted here for poor health.

224
00:15:06,046 --> 00:15:09,846
But, you're worried about
what happened to your bike?

225
00:15:10,203 --> 00:15:13,306
You've brought the right person.
- Sorry, sir.

226
00:15:13,603 --> 00:15:14,766
She's bothersome.

227
00:15:15,926 --> 00:15:16,766
Sir.

228
00:15:18,926 --> 00:15:19,966
Where is she?

229
00:15:20,553 --> 00:15:22,246
She has gone to pay the bill.

230
00:15:22,381 --> 00:15:24,634
Oh..
- Sir, don't worry.

231
00:15:24,846 --> 00:15:26,446
How can I not worry?

232
00:15:26,713 --> 00:15:28,086
It was our first date.

233
00:15:29,646 --> 00:15:30,966
And it went like this.

234
00:15:31,433 --> 00:15:33,283
I was happy since morning.

235
00:15:33,446 --> 00:15:34,966
But, I am in the hospital now.

236
00:15:35,413 --> 00:15:37,966
Don't cry, the day is not over yet.

237
00:15:39,003 --> 00:15:40,486
Shall we do one thing?

238
00:15:40,993 --> 00:15:42,952
You leave first.

239
00:15:43,752 --> 00:15:45,686
We will follow you, okay?

240
00:15:47,282 --> 00:15:50,742
But, maintain some privacy, man.

241
00:15:52,036 --> 00:15:53,163
My ill luck!

242
00:15:53,693 --> 00:15:56,195
Is everything okay?
- I am okay.

243
00:15:56,243 --> 00:15:58,835
You are smiling happily,
but I am scared.

244
00:15:58,883 --> 00:16:01,725
It's okay, I am fine.
- Can you ride?

245
00:16:01,773 --> 00:16:03,363
Yes.
- Shall I ride? - No.

246
00:16:03,446 --> 00:16:06,086
I will ride.
- Are you sure? - Yes.

247
00:16:06,343 --> 00:16:09,052
We are their love gurus.

248
00:16:09,638 --> 00:16:11,161
Come on, pose.
- Hey, no.

249
00:16:12,015 --> 00:16:13,831
I want my bike back safe and sound.

250
00:16:14,043 --> 00:16:16,606
If not, I will tell my dad
and deduct it from your salary.

251
00:16:17,963 --> 00:16:20,003
Hey, don't do that.

252
00:16:20,406 --> 00:16:21,726
Why are you doing this?

253
00:16:24,046 --> 00:16:26,926
They're leaving.. Start the bike.
- Get on.

254
00:16:31,006 --> 00:16:35,166
Go fast.
- I am going. - Accelerate..

255
00:16:56,643 --> 00:16:59,006
Hey, go.
- I am hungry.

256
00:16:59,103 --> 00:17:00,206
Please go.

257
00:17:00,926 --> 00:17:02,566
You are doing too much.
- Go.

258
00:17:08,766 --> 00:17:10,046
I went inside.

259
00:17:10,966 --> 00:17:12,683
It's okay
even if he had scolded me.

260
00:17:13,286 --> 00:17:15,326
He insulted me
by showing some actions.

261
00:17:16,566 --> 00:17:17,806
Don't feel bad.

262
00:17:17,862 --> 00:17:21,283
You just want to get
scolded, right? You little..

263
00:17:22,326 --> 00:17:24,646
You were waiting for the chance?
- Yes.

264
00:17:24,882 --> 00:17:28,446
Wearing the chef's coat makes you
feel like scolding someone. - Hello.

265
00:17:28,883 --> 00:17:29,806
Enough.

266
00:17:32,086 --> 00:17:34,966
I can't believe I had to witness
this, and in this heat.

267
00:17:53,926 --> 00:17:56,086
Show this.
- What material is this?

268
00:17:56,494 --> 00:17:58,214
What other colours are available?

269
00:17:59,286 --> 00:18:01,846
Show that. What material is that?
- Hey.

270
00:18:02,283 --> 00:18:05,646
Why are you looking here?
Get lost..

271
00:18:08,483 --> 00:18:11,723
This is superb, right?
- Good, very nice.

272
00:18:12,833 --> 00:18:16,086
I like this colour too.
- Very nice, wait..

273
00:18:20,443 --> 00:18:22,966
Is it good? You like it?
- Oh, God.

274
00:18:23,647 --> 00:18:25,840
I don't know
what else I have to see.

275
00:18:28,886 --> 00:18:32,926
Hey, isn't it fun to watch them?
- Yes, it'll be.

276
00:18:33,246 --> 00:18:35,126
Do you know what you are doing?

277
00:18:36,326 --> 00:18:37,963
You just keep watching.
I am leaving.

278
00:18:38,033 --> 00:18:39,286
Hello, wait.

279
00:18:39,846 --> 00:18:41,846
No, it's okay.
- Sir, is it done?

280
00:18:42,043 --> 00:18:44,926
Hey, wait, don't disturb us.
- Oh, God..

281
00:18:45,726 --> 00:18:47,006
Okay, carry on.

282
00:18:47,846 --> 00:18:48,966
Give them a minute.

283
00:18:50,173 --> 00:18:52,293
Okay..
- Nice.

284
00:18:52,553 --> 00:18:54,966
Really?
- They're done, let's go.

285
00:18:58,743 --> 00:19:00,966
Okay, sir.
- Thank you. - Sit.

286
00:19:01,683 --> 00:19:03,806
Hey, sit properly.

287
00:19:34,566 --> 00:19:39,646
I loved riding the bike
and exploring all day.

288
00:19:43,886 --> 00:19:48,046
I went on a bike after many days.
That too with you.

289
00:19:50,366 --> 00:19:53,326
I enjoyed a lot.
- Actually..

290
00:19:54,487 --> 00:19:56,810
It's been a long time
since I felt happy.

291
00:19:59,126 --> 00:20:00,406
Thank you very much.

292
00:20:01,286 --> 00:20:05,126
Did I help you?
You are thanking me.

293
00:20:06,083 --> 00:20:10,846
We went outing,
we enjoyed together, that's it.

294
00:20:11,726 --> 00:20:15,763
I can't forget this day.
Not only that.

295
00:20:16,603 --> 00:20:22,486
I'll never forget meeting
and talking to you in college.

296
00:20:23,446 --> 00:20:26,526
You could have told me
all this back then.

297
00:20:27,062 --> 00:20:29,502
The only question on my mind
all day today..

298
00:20:29,606 --> 00:20:30,592
was that one.

299
00:20:32,606 --> 00:20:37,726
I still regret
not doing that, Padma.

300
00:20:39,532 --> 00:20:42,772
Anyway, it's not too late.

301
00:20:43,766 --> 00:20:47,606
Actually, Joji, that is..
- Mom.

302
00:21:00,845 --> 00:21:02,125
What are you doing?

303
00:21:02,303 --> 00:21:05,006
Nothing, Shruthi.
We were just talking.

304
00:21:05,966 --> 00:21:07,246
Aren't you ashamed?

305
00:21:13,446 --> 00:21:16,646
How old are you?
What are you doing here?

306
00:21:20,203 --> 00:21:22,126
You told me that you were
going to a Siddha doctor.

307
00:21:22,576 --> 00:21:24,526
I have been calling you
repeatedly for three hours.

308
00:21:24,853 --> 00:21:26,253
You are not answering the phone.

309
00:21:32,123 --> 00:21:34,006
Shruthi, just listen to me.

310
00:21:36,715 --> 00:21:38,355
I've run out of patience.

311
00:21:40,677 --> 00:21:44,517
I might end up yelling at you.
You better go to your room.

312
00:22:26,683 --> 00:22:28,606
Poor guy, Pandi.

313
00:22:30,977 --> 00:22:32,697
He became sad
when she spoke like that.

314
00:22:34,646 --> 00:22:36,126
I feel so bad.

315
00:22:39,563 --> 00:22:42,083
If a man is unlucky
throughout his life..

316
00:22:43,281 --> 00:22:44,721
what will he do?

317
00:22:46,646 --> 00:22:48,726
Her daughter said
such unpleasant things.

318
00:22:49,406 --> 00:22:52,166
It's true
that rich people lack peace.

319
00:22:53,073 --> 00:22:57,006
How long has it been since
I asked for a full boiled egg?

320
00:22:57,406 --> 00:22:58,926
He is making an omelette.

321
00:22:59,766 --> 00:23:01,246
What the heck are you doing?

322
00:23:01,603 --> 00:23:03,326
Hey, this is not for you.

323
00:23:06,243 --> 00:23:08,246
Do you see with your eyes closed?

324
00:23:09,286 --> 00:23:11,406
Here is the full boiled egg.
Pandi, give it to me.

325
00:23:12,286 --> 00:23:14,166
Here you go.
- Hey.

326
00:23:14,933 --> 00:23:16,486
Why are you
talking disrespectfully?

327
00:23:16,766 --> 00:23:18,086
Won't I get angry then?

328
00:23:18,526 --> 00:23:20,883
You won't respect us,
but should we respect you?

329
00:23:21,163 --> 00:23:22,046
That's right.

330
00:23:22,406 --> 00:23:25,285
Hey, I'm speaking very politely.

331
00:23:25,333 --> 00:23:28,366
Yes, he is very decent.
Congratulations.

332
00:23:30,287 --> 00:23:33,247
Hey, don't mess with me.

333
00:23:33,886 --> 00:23:37,286
Then I'll be a different person.
- Will he be decent at least?

334
00:23:38,646 --> 00:23:41,366
Or is he also a drunkard like you?
- Hey!

335
00:23:42,286 --> 00:23:44,406
Are you laughing?
Hey.

336
00:23:44,526 --> 00:23:46,486
You don't know who I am.

337
00:23:46,806 --> 00:23:50,086
I will destroy this shop.
- Oh.

338
00:23:50,433 --> 00:23:53,526
As if he is a magic man,
he'll change the shop by magic.

339
00:23:53,723 --> 00:23:56,846
Hey..
- Hey, take your hands off him!

340
00:23:57,459 --> 00:23:59,736
Why are you being disrespectful?
- Take your hands off.

341
00:23:59,858 --> 00:24:00,979
Hey, leave.

342
00:24:01,233 --> 00:24:03,972
Why are you pushing me?
Take your hands off.

343
00:24:04,020 --> 00:24:05,112
Hey.

344
00:24:05,766 --> 00:24:08,246
Why are you raising your hand
when we're talking?

345
00:24:09,646 --> 00:24:10,726
I will kill you.

346
00:24:11,153 --> 00:24:13,806
Hey, don't..

347
00:24:14,846 --> 00:24:17,366
Don't..
- Hey, you are drunk. Go away.

348
00:24:18,806 --> 00:24:20,686
Hey.
- Go away. - Hey.

349
00:24:21,326 --> 00:24:22,926
You hit me, right?

350
00:24:24,643 --> 00:24:26,446
Tomorrow, the shop won't be there.

351
00:24:27,599 --> 00:24:30,325
Tomorrow, you will know
who I am. - Yes, I'll know.

352
00:24:30,446 --> 00:24:31,766
I will see you tomorrow.

353
00:24:31,893 --> 00:24:33,886
The shop won't be there tomorrow.

354
00:24:34,013 --> 00:24:36,846
The shop won't be there tomorrow.
- Sir, wait..

355
00:24:37,433 --> 00:24:39,726
Hey..

356
00:24:39,993 --> 00:24:41,686
Why did you fight with him?

357
00:24:42,526 --> 00:24:44,646
He hit me and tried to strangle me.

358
00:24:45,326 --> 00:24:47,166
He is a drunkard.
- Hey.

359
00:24:47,333 --> 00:24:49,006
He works in the corporation office.

360
00:24:49,133 --> 00:24:51,406
He comes to the shop often
and creates problems.

361
00:24:51,593 --> 00:24:53,352
So, I avoid
any kind of trouble with him.

362
00:24:53,526 --> 00:24:56,926
If he gets tense,
he will wreck the shop.

363
00:24:57,573 --> 00:24:59,446
Oh, no.

364
00:24:59,526 --> 00:25:01,446
I shouldn't have left the shop.

365
00:25:01,753 --> 00:25:02,793
Hey.

366
00:25:02,959 --> 00:25:06,592
His actions have already caused
two-three shops to change places.

367
00:25:06,966 --> 00:25:09,123
It's been a year and still
they can't reopen their shops.

368
00:25:09,326 --> 00:25:11,326
And you've caused
problems with him.

369
00:25:11,973 --> 00:25:15,646
Over! Everything is over!

370
00:25:15,973 --> 00:25:18,446
Hey, he will make us
remove the shop.
